trans-unit.source: Represents the SharePoint project.
trans-unit.target: 表示 SharePoint 项目。

trans-unit.source: Gets or set the name of the deployment configuration to use for deployment.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置用于部署的部署配置的名称。

trans-unit.source: The value should be from a list of available deployment configurations on the system.
trans-unit.target: 该值应来自于系统上的可用部署配置列表。

trans-unit.source: The name of a deployment configuration.
trans-unit.target: 部署配置的名称。

trans-unit.source: Gets a language specific project type GUID that used to return add item templates.
trans-unit.target: 获取用于返回添加项模板的语言特定项目类型 GUID。

trans-unit.source: A GUID representing a project type.
trans-unit.target: 一个表示项目类型的 GUID。

trans-unit.source: This GUID that can be used as a language string in <xref:EnvDTE80.Solution2.GetProjectItemTemplate%2A> function to retrieve a path to a template.
trans-unit.target: 可以用作语言字符串在此 GUID<xref:EnvDTE80.Solution2.GetProjectItemTemplate%2A>函数可检索到模板的路径。

trans-unit.source: Typically, <xref:EnvDTE80.Solution2.GetProjectItemTemplate%2A> accepts a language string such as "CSharp" or "VB" to retrieve a language-specific template.
trans-unit.target: 通常情况下，<xref:EnvDTE80.Solution2.GetProjectItemTemplate%2A>接受如"CSharp"或"VB"可检索特定于语言的模板语言字符串。

trans-unit.source: SharePoint projects use GUIDs instead of strings to hide SharePoint project item templates from non-SharePoint projects.
trans-unit.target: SharePoint 项目而不是字符串使用 Guid 来隐藏非 SharePoint 项目中的 SharePoint 项目项模板。

trans-unit.source: Gets the application specific settings of the project.
trans-unit.target: 获取项目的应用程序指定设置。

trans-unit.source: The application specific settings of the project.
trans-unit.target: 该项目的应用程序指定设置。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets where the project should be deployed on the server: either "Bin" or "GAC".
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置应在服务器上部署项目的位置：“Bin”或“GAC”。

trans-unit.source: The location where the assembly is deployed.
trans-unit.target: 部署程序集的位置。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether the solution is retracted after debugging.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置是否在调试后收回解决方案。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the assembly is automatically retracted after debugging; <see langword="false" /> otherwise.
trans-unit.target: 如果要在调试后自动收回程序集，则为 <see langword="True" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: By default, the SharePoint solution is retracted from SharePoint after debugging completes.
trans-unit.target: 默认情况下，SharePoint 解决方案在调试完成后从 SharePoint 收回。

trans-unit.source: However, setting this property to `false` enables you to prevent the solution from being retracted after debugging.
trans-unit.target: 但是，将此属性设置为`false`，可防止该解决方案在调试后被撤消。

trans-unit.source: This property is exposed as the **Auto-retract after debugging** option in the **SharePoint** tab of the SharePoint project property page.
trans-unit.target: 此属性公开为**调试后自动收回**选项**SharePoint** SharePoint 项目属性页选项卡。

trans-unit.source: A dictionary of all deployment configurations, including user-defined and in-the-box deployment configurations.
trans-unit.target: 所有部署配置的字典，包括用户定义的部署配置和现有部署配置。

trans-unit.source: An object representing deployment configurations.
trans-unit.target: 一个表示部署配置的对象。

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of SharePoint features defined in the project.
trans-unit.target: 获取项目中定义的 SharePoint 功能的集合。

trans-unit.source: A collection of SharePoint features.
trans-unit.target: SharePoint 功能的集合。

trans-unit.source: Gets the ID of the project.
trans-unit.target: 获取项目的 ID。

trans-unit.source: An ID value for the project.
trans-unit.target: 项目的 ID 值。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether the project assembly should be packaged.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置是否应打包项目程序集。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the assembly should be packaged; <see langword="false" /> otherwise.
trans-unit.target: 如果程序集应打包，则为 <see langword="True" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets value whether project's package is deployed as a sandboxed solution or as a farm solution.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个值，指示应将项目包部署为沙盒解决方案还是场解决方案。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if the project is a sandboxed solution; <see langword="false" /> otherwise.
trans-unit.target: 如果该项目是沙盒解决方案，则为 <see langword="True" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether Silverlight debugging is enabled.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置是否启用 Silverlight 调试。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="True" /> if Silverlight debugging is enabled; <see langword="false" /> otherwise.
trans-unit.target: 如果启用 Silverlight 调试，则为 <see langword="True" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets value indicating whether Workflow debugging is enabled.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个值，该值指示是否启用工作流调试。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the Workflow debugging is enabled; Otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果启用工作流调试，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of mapped folders in the project.
trans-unit.target: 获取项目中映射文件夹的集合。

trans-unit.source: A collection of mapped folders.
trans-unit.target: 映射文件夹的集合。

trans-unit.source: Gets the project's assembly full path after compilation.
trans-unit.target: 获取编译之后的项目程序集完整路径。

trans-unit.source: A string representing a project assembly path.
trans-unit.target: 一个表示项目程序集路径的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets an instance of the SharePoint package associated with the project.
trans-unit.target: 获取与项目关联的 SharePoint 包的实例。

trans-unit.source: An instance of a package.
trans-unit.target: 程序包的实例。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the command line that runs after deployment.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置在部署之后运行的命令行。

trans-unit.source: A string representing a command line.
trans-unit.target: 一个表示命令行的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the command line that runs before deployment.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置在部署之前运行的命令行。

trans-unit.source: A string representing a command line.
trans-unit.target: 一个表示命令行的字符串。

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of SharePoint project items in the project.
trans-unit.target: 获取项目中的 SharePoint 项目项的集合。

trans-unit.source: A collection of project items.
trans-unit.target: 项目项的集合。

trans-unit.source: Gets the current project system mode.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前项目系统模式。

trans-unit.source: Check <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointProjectMode" /> for possible values.
trans-unit.target: 有关可能的值，请查阅 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointProjectMode" />。

trans-unit.source: The current project system mode.
trans-unit.target: 当前项目系统模式。

trans-unit.source: Gets an instance of the SharePoint Project Service.
trans-unit.target: 获取 SharePoint 项目服务的实例。

trans-unit.source: An instance of the SharePoint project service.
trans-unit.target: SharePoint 项目服务的一个实例。

trans-unit.source: Gets read and write data associated with the SharePoint project in the project user file.
trans-unit.target: 获取项目用户文件中与 SharePoint 项目关联的读取和写入数据。

trans-unit.source: An object representing user file data.
trans-unit.target: 一个表示用户文件数据的对象。

trans-unit.source: For more information about using this property to persist data in SharePoint project, see [Saving Data in Extensions of the SharePoint Project System](/visualstudio/sharepoint/saving-data-in-extensions-of-the-sharepoint-project-system.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关使用此属性将数据保持在 SharePoint 项目的详细信息，请参阅[扩展 SharePoint 项目系统中保存数据](/visualstudio/sharepoint/saving-data-in-extensions-of-the-sharepoint-project-system.md)。

trans-unit.source: Gets a list of SharePoint project items selected in **Solution Explorer**.
trans-unit.target: 获取在“解决方案资源管理器”中选择的 SharePoint 项目项的列表。

trans-unit.source: A collection of project items.
trans-unit.target: 项目项的集合。

trans-unit.source: Gets the SharePoint connection instance that enables users to execute commands against the SharePoint object model in the vssphost.exe 64-bit process.
trans-unit.target: 获取 SharePoint 连接实例，该实例使用户能在 vssphost.exe 64 位进程中针对 SharePoint 对象模型执行命令。

trans-unit.source: An instance of a SharePoint connection.
trans-unit.target: SharePoint 连接的一个实例。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Site URL used by project during design time, deployment and debugging.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置项目在设计阶段、部署和调试期间使用的站点 URL。

trans-unit.source: A URL for a SharePoint site.
trans-unit.target: SharePoint 网站的 URL。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the item to launch on project startup.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置要在项目启动时启动的项。

trans-unit.source: An object representing a project item.
trans-unit.target: 一个表示项目项的对象。

trans-unit.source: Gets the Url to launch on project startup.
trans-unit.target: 获取要在项目启动时启动的 URL。

trans-unit.source: A URL.
trans-unit.target: 一个 URL。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject.StartupItem%2A> exposes a non-null absolute Url, use that.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject.StartupItem%2A>公开非 null 的绝对 Url，使用。

trans-unit.source: If the `StartupItem` exposes a non-null, relative Url, combine it with the `SiteUrl`.
trans-unit.target: 如果`StartupItem`公开非 null，相对 Url，将其与结合`SiteUrl`。

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, default to the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject.SiteUrl%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 否则，默认为<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProject.SiteUrl%2A>。

trans-unit.source: Applies any pending add item events to the SharePoint project object model to synchronize it with the DTE object model.
trans-unit.target: 向 SharePoint 项目对象模型应用任何挂起的添加项事件，以使其与 DTE 对象模型同步。

trans-unit.source: This method is typically called in a project or item template wizard before accessing the SharePoint project object model.
trans-unit.target: 此方法通常称为项目或项模板向导中之前访问 SharePoint 项目对象模型。

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the SharePoint project object model will be updated when the template wizard is finished.
trans-unit.target: 否则，在模板向导完成后，将更新 SharePoint 项目对象模型。

trans-unit.source: Gets the required SharePoint or Office version: "14.0" or "15.0".
trans-unit.target: 获取所需的 SharePoint 或 Office 版本：“14.0”或“15.0”。

trans-unit.source: Default to 14.0.
The required SharePoint or Office version.
trans-unit.target: 所需的 SharePoint 或 Office 版本。
